          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 flex flex-col gap-1 text-[11px] text-[var(--fg-muted)]">
            <li><strong>Concrete:</strong> ACI 318 Building Code &mdash; volume formulas per ASTM C138/C172 standards</li>
            <li><strong>Roofing:</strong> NRCA Roofing Manual &mdash; pitch multipliers per ANSI/SPRI; coverage from Owens Corning, GAF, CertainTeed</li>
            <li><strong>Paint:</strong> ASTM D16 standard &mdash; coverage rates from Sherwin-Williams, Behr, PPG</li>
            <li><strong>Tile:</strong> TCNA Handbook for Ceramic, Glass, and Stone Tile Installation &mdash; waste factors per pattern</li>
            <li><strong>Weight:</strong> Material densities per ASTM C138 (concrete), AISC Manual (steel), published lumber species data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--fg-muted)]">
          Assumptions and limitations are stated on each calculator page. Always verify final quantities against the specific products you purchase and consult a licensed contractor for structural work. <strong>Last updated:</strong> July&nbsp;2026
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>
